Sample PPT templates are stored in Azure Blob Storage.

Their content is embedded using OpenAI Text Embedding 3 Large.

The embeddings are saved in ChromaDB (local folder inside the repo).

Design elements from template PPTs are extracted and saved as JSON in a design_json folder.

python-pptx is used to generate the final PowerPoint slides.

GPT-5 Mini generates slide text/content.

Image 1 Mini generates any images needed for slides.

Streamlit UI provides a simple front-end for users to interact with the app.
